{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901B0325P0D1N001841", "chronotag": "1739874603139", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "1841", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1841", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901B0325P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0325", "triAmendement": "oeaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabdzy", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795318", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845413", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Boyard"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 29", "articleDesignationCourte": "APR\u00c8S ART. 29", "articleDesignation": "APR\u00c8S L'ARTICLE 29, ins\u00e9rer l'article suivant:", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "Apr\u00e8s", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "true", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0325.asp#D_Article_29"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>Dans un d&#x00E9;lai de six mois &#x00E0; compter de la promulgation de la pr&#x00E9;sente loi, le Gouvernement remet au Parlement un rapport portant sur l&#x2019;application de l&#x2019;article 100 de la loi n&#x00B0; 2021-1754 du 23 d&#x00E9;cembre 2021 de financement de la s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; sociale pour 2022.</p><p>Ce rapport s&#x2019;attache notamment &#x00E0; &#x00E9;valuer l&#x2019;opportunit&#x00E9; d&#x2019;une suppression de la condition d&#x2019;isolement du parent ayant la charge de l&#x2019;enfant pour lequel l&#x2019;allocation de soutien familial est vers&#x00E9;e.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement propose une demande de rapport sur la d&#x00E9;conjugalisation de l&#x2019;allocation de soutien familial en supprimant la condition relative &#x00E0; l&#x2019;isolement du parent assumant la charge de l&#x2019;enfant &#x2013; soit g&#x00E9;n&#x00E9;ralement la m&#x00E8;re. En effet, aujourd&#x2019;hui, si ce parent se marie, se pacse ou m&#x00EA;me seulement reprend une vie en concubinage, il perd le droit &#x00E0; percevoir l&#x2019;ASF. Cela g&#x00E9;n&#x00E8;re une situation de d&#x00E9;pendance du parent isol&#x00E9; vis-&#x00E0;-vis de son nouveau conjoint, alors m&#x00EA;me que le b&#x00E9;n&#x00E9;fice de l&#x2019;ASF est attach&#x00E9; &#x00E0; l&#x2019;enfant.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-25", "datePublication": "2024-11-05", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B0325P0D1N001841?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "Z3", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "73500", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}